member.name: PRINTPAGERANGE
member.summary: Represents a range of pages in a print job. A print job can have more than one page range. This information is supplied in the structure when calling the PrintDlgEx function.

member.name: PRINTPAGERANGE.nFromPage
member.summary: The first page of the range.

member.name: PRINTPAGERANGE.nToPage
member.summary: The last page of the range.
